  {{#smd-page-body}}

    <p>SMD contains a fab component to create fab buttons positioned at the bottom of your app.</p>

    <p>The fab component can be placed at the application route and controlled at route level by the smd-fab-service. This allows easy fixed positioning of the button.</p>

    <div class="sg-flex-row">
